high_descs: Walk to the counter on the right
Open the cabinet on top, take the plate out, close the cabinet
Put the plate in the sink, turn on the faucet to wash the plate, turn off the faucet, take the clean plate
Turn around, walk to the refrigerator on the left
Open the refrigerator, put the plate by the egg, close the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: Wash the plate from the cabinet, put it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Take a half step to your right and then walk to the counter in front of you.
Open the cabinets that are hanging in front of you on the wall and take out the plate you see there.
Take a couple steps to your left so you are facing the sink.
Clean the plate in the sink then turn the faucet off and pick the plate back up.
Now turn around and walk to the fridge.
Put the plate on the shelf with the egg slightly in front of and to the right of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Move to the counter right of the sink.
Pick up the dirty plate from the cabinet above the counter.
Bring the dirty plate to the sink.
Wash the plate in the sink.
Bring the cleaned plate to the fridge.
Put the cleaned plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned plate in the fridge.
